Entry.JapaneseText: <Mao>のフォルス感知能力が高いのは、聖獣たちに 生み出された事と関係があるのかもしれんな。
Entry.EnglishText: I'm guessing the reason why you can sense Force so well is because you were made by the Sacred Beasts.

Entry.JapaneseText: ……ねえ、<Eugene>…… ボクのコト、嫌いになった？
Entry.EnglishText: ...Y'know, <Eugene>... Do you not like me anymore?

Entry.JapaneseText: ……何を言っているんだ？ 嫌いになる理由がどこにある？
Entry.EnglishText: ...What has you saying that? What reason would I have to dislike you?

Entry.JapaneseText: <Veigue>の言う通り、おまえはおまえだ。 これまでと何も変わらん……ちがうか？
Entry.EnglishText: It's as <Veigue> said, you are you. Nothing has changed from before... Am I incorrect?

Entry.JapaneseText: ホントウ……？ ホントウにそう思う？
おまえらしくないぞ……それとも、 おまえが俺を嫌いになったのか？
Entry.EnglishText: That's rather unlike you... Well, on that note, do you not like <Italic>me</Italic> anymore?

Entry.JapaneseText: もおっ、<Eugene>なんて嫌いだぁ！
